metadata.name: Nifty Pass
metadata.description: The Nifty Pass is the utility NFT by Nifty.io used throughout the Nifty.io ecosystem. Each Nifty Pass grants you access to the Community Creation Platform and whitelists you for all future projects developed by the Nifty.io team and community. Furthermore, each Nifty Pass provides a discount on every project by Nifty.io.
